{"tid":2088891,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美心伙拍Shake Shack進軍華南 預計2030年前於中國開設55家分店","createTime":"2020-07-01T11:42:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T12:17:19.000Z","uid":53026,"like":2,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"60b7e6a6e05b96f45b12e8f0e34852411196c3e0","tid":2088891,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T11:42:09.000Z","msg":"美心伙拍Shake Shack進軍華南 預計2030年前於中國開設55家分店<br />\n<br />\n文章日期：2020年7月1日 16:12<br />\nShare<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/fin/20200701/s00010/5ebd7ca4a83b4daa97d140850fd91f2a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2F20200701%2Fs00010%2F5ebd7ca4a83b4daa97d140850fd91f2a.jpg&h=a0388fc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖1之1 - <br />\n美心伙拍Shake Shack進軍華南 預計2030年前於中國開設55家分店<br />\n<br />\n美國漢堡速食店集團Shake Shack公布，將與香港美心食品合作進軍華南地區，並於在深圳開設首間門店。<br />\n<br />\nShake Shack指，深圳分店為品牌的首家華南門店，預計2030年前，在華南開設至少15家分店，目標城市包括深圳、廣州、福州和廈門等，全國則開設55家分店。<br />\n<br />\n根據Shake Shack官方網頁，目前全港共有6家Shake Shack 分店。"},{"pid":"e411283d8c37a01c6ad9972715ddbbac8d13f441","tid":2088891,"uid":53026,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T11:42:47.000Z","msg":"原來香港唔算係華南？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家先「進軍」？"},{"pid":"88a0351a79a2ce127d28557b8b70fd0df7030a36","tid":2088891,"uid":11291,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T11:43:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之後大陸就會有間叫shack shake"},{"pid":"a7e1b9b721d77825311be5ff9508aca65498d92b","ti